2 id=use-a-starter>Use a starter</h2><ul class=Starter-list><li class=\"Starter-item Starter\"><img class=Starter-image src=/img/starter/startbootstrap-clean-blog.png alt=metalsmith/startbootstrap-clean-blog width=128 height=96><p class=Starter-title>metalsmith/startbootstrap-clean-blog<br><a class=Starter-link--source href=https://github.com/metalsmith/startbootstrap-clean-blog>Code</a>| <a class=Starter-link--demo href=https://startbootstrap.github.io/startbootstrap-clean-blog/ >Demo</a></p><pre class=\"hljs language-plaintext\"><code>git clone https://github.com/metalsmith/startbootstrap-clean-blogcd startbootstrap-clean-blog && npm install</code></pre></li><li class=\"Starter-item Starter\"><img class=Starter-image src=/img/starter/bare-bones-starter.png alt=wernerglinka/metalsmith-bare-bones-starter width=128 height=96><p class=Starter-title>wernerglinka/metalsmith-bare-bones-starter<br><a class=Starter-link--source href=https://github.com/wernerglinka/metalsmith-bare-bones-starter>Code</a>| <a class=Starter-link--demo href=https://metalsmith-bare-bones-starter.netlify.app/ >Demo</a></p><pre class=\"hljs language-plaintext\"><code>git clone https://github.com/wernerglinka/metalsmith-bare-bones-startercd metalsmith-bare-bones-starter && npm install</code></pre></li><li class=\"Starter-item Starter\"><img class=Starter-image src=/img/starter/blog-starter.png alt=wernerglinka/metalsmith-blog-starter width=128 height=96><p class=Starter-title>wernerglinka/metalsmith-blog-starter<br><a class=Starter-link--source href=https://github.com/wernerglinka/metalsmith-blog-starter>Code</a>| <a class=Starter-link--demo href=https://metalsmith-blog-starter.netlify.app/ >Demo</a></p><pre class=\"hljs language-plaintext\"><code>git clone https://github.com/wernerglinka/metalsmith-blog-startercd metalsmith-blog-starter && npm install</code></pre></li><li class=\"Starter-item Starter\"><img class=Starter-image src=/img/starter/company-starter.png alt=wernerglinka/metalsmith-compan